{
  "stem": "8610.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We weren't prepared psychologically to be able to deal with a problem as vast as this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, if I, as a Jew, wasn't prepared as it were-- although I knew that, that these things have been happening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We'd, we'd got the news from 1942 onwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We heard about Auschwitz and the destruction of the communities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But for these non-Jewish chaps, to them it was utterly new.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I can, in a way, sympathize with them because they didn't understand the situation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was too big for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And sometimes a situation which is-- goes out of hand, it's because people aren't equipped to deal with it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They weren't trained for this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Military government wasn't trained for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I give you a simple example.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the early days of the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was very concerned.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We needed help.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There was only two-- there were only two chaplains in the whole of Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I knew that the Jewish refugees-- the Jewish committee for relief abroad had a team in Holland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we needed help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I rushed out to Brussels to the headquarters of military government-- or civil affairs, they called it in those days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, look, this team in, in, in Holland, really hasn't got enough work to do.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we need them desperately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this young major-- same rank as myself, so I could talk to him quite openly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, well, you see, Padre, you see that map?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He shows me a map with pins on it over the place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He says, these are all camps which exist in Europe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As far as we're concerned, it's an academic problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I said, I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Academic?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
